      "date": "2019-06-13 05:30:50.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nYS, no need to add Gerrit Gatekeeper to patches.  They will appear on Oleg's list for landing once they have two positive reviews and Verified +1 from Maloo and Jenkins.  Patches that are ready to land are added to the master-next branch to have extra integration testing for about 3 days, and are then landed if there aren't other problems found.  This means it may be about a week from when a patch is ready for landing until it actually lands.",
